00:20:31.500 --> 00:20:33.450 align:middle
Everyone, fall back!

00:20:33.450 --> 00:20:37.380 align:middle
Take refuge in Momiji's room 
before she can launch an attack!

00:20:40.010 --> 00:20:41.910 align:middle
You too, Miyo-chan! Hurry!

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:44.930 align:middle
I can't. I'm...

00:20:46.600 --> 00:20:48.800 align:middle
My eyes are locked on, and I can't move!

00:20:52.730 --> 00:20:54.530 align:middle
