00:20:54.530 --> 00:20:57.400 align:middle
Miyo-chan!

00:21:04.820 --> 00:21:05.880 align:middle
She's awake!

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:08.080 align:middle
A-Are you all right?

00:21:08.080 --> 00:21:09.630 align:middle
Huh?

00:21:09.630 --> 00:21:12.700 align:middle
What happened just now?

00:21:14.430 --> 00:21:17.390 align:middle
You're banned from alcohol 
for life, that's what.

00:21:20.930 --> 00:21:22.720 align:middle
Onee-sama!

00:21:40.850 --> 00:21:44.850 align:middle
It's been a while since we've gotten 
to spend New Year's like this, huh?

00:21:44.850 --> 00:21:46.580 align:middle
You're right.

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:51.160 align:middle
So what exactly did you pray 
for back at the shrine?

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:53.630 align:middle
What? Uh... It's a secret.

00:21:53.630 --> 00:21:55.190 align:middle
But I wanna know!

00:21:55.190 --> 00:21:56.640 align:middle
Come on, tell me!

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:57.870 align:middle
Quit nagging!

00:21:57.870 --> 00:21:59.030 align:middle
Honestly...

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:01.930 align:middle
I haven't the faintest idea.

